definition: horse/CL:匹[pi3]/horse or cavalry piece in Chinese chess/knight in Western chess
surname Ma/abbr. for Malaysia 馬來西亞|马来西亚[Ma3 lai2 xi1 ya4]
he or him/(used for either sex when the sex is unknown or unimportant)/(used before sb's name for emphasis)/(used as a meaningless mock object)/other/another

sentences.english: In 1814, Malta became a part of the British Empire.
sentences.chinese: 1814年，马耳他岛沦为大英帝国的殖民地。

sentences.english: Malta holds a referendum on whether to allow divorce.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他就是否允许离婚举行全民公决。

sentences.english: The Maltese are used to strange visitors invading their homeland.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他人已经习惯了陌生游客的蜂拥而至。

sentences.english: VALLETTA, Malta – How things have changed.
The Republic of Malta is a small and densely-populated island nation in southern Europe.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他共和国是欧洲南部一个人口密集的小国。

sentences.english: Malta is the smallest EU country in terms of both population and area.
sentences.chinese: 就人口和面积而言，马耳他是欧盟中最小的国家。

sentences.english: 1964 - Malta becomes independent from the United Kingdom.
sentences.chinese: 1964年的今天，马耳他脱离英国独立。

sentences.english: No Maltese athlete has won an Olympic medal to date.
sentences.chinese: 至今马耳他还未获得奥运奖牌。

sentences.english: And when they were escaped, then they knew that the island was called Melita.
sentences.chinese: 我们既已得救，才知道那岛名叫马耳他。

sentences.english: The last round they won 4 to 0 smoothly Malta, into the playoff.
sentences.chinese: 最后一轮他们4比0顺利拿下马耳他，进入附加赛。

sentences.english: The President of the Republic is elected every five years by the House of Representatives.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他共和国的总统每五年由议院代表选举产生。

sentences.english: The Maltese nobility was established during this period.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他人的高贵气质就是在这一时期形成的。

sentences.english: One the favourite Maltese sports is shooting or trapping anything that flies.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他人最喜爱的体育活动之一是射击和捕鸟。

sentences.english: Support for the Yes vote has fallen sharply according to a latest survey of Malta.
sentences.chinese: 马耳他的一项最新调查显示，赞成者已在急速减少。

sentences.english: Many Maltese avidly follow English football matches.
sentences.chinese: 许多马耳他人热衷于英式足球比赛。

sentences.english: Shaolin monks perform Chinese Kung Fu in Malta.
sentences.chinese: 少林和尚在马耳他表演中国功夫。
